data.description: This is your chance to own a charming 2 story home with an open floorpan and a great backyard in a popular subdivision! The 2 story entry foyer with upgraded spindle staircase sets the tone for this home! You will find a normal dining room, sitting room/office and spacious living room all on the main level. The oversized laundry room will not disappoint! Upstairs you will find a spacious owners suite and 3 secondary bedrooms! This home offers ample closet space for all of your storage needs!
